title: Monthly Contributor Payment (November)
body:
This proposal is just to establish a record of November payments for the working group contributors listed below. Each contributor belongs to Rarible Dao working groups on an ongoing basis and has already submitted a previous proposal which has been accepted through November.

Noah (Ops): $4,000
Sarmad (Ops): $6,000
Mariana (Marketing): $5,000
Stefan (Dev) : $8100
Zak (Dev): $16,600
Brandon (Dev): $16,600
